CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Nicolet Bankshares Inc is registered with the U.S. Security and Exchange Commission and incorporated in the state of Wisconsin. Nicolet Bankshares Inc is primarely in the business of national commercial banks. For financial reporting, their fiscal year ends on December 31st. This page includes all SEC registration details as well as a list of all documents (S-1, Prospectus, Current Reports, 8-K, 10K, Annual Reports) filed by Nicolet Bankshares Inc. Nicolet Bankshares Inc is a US-based bank holding company. The bank offers various commercial banking services in Northeastern Wisconsin and the Upper Peninsula of Michigan. Its principal business is banking, consisting of lending and deposit gathering, as well as ancillary banking-related products and services, to businesses and individuals of the communities it serves, and the operational support to deliver, fund and manage such banking products and services.
